<li><a href="/wiki/Drew_Barrymore" title="Drew Barrymore">Drew Barrymore</a> as Margaret Jessup</li>
<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Megan_Jeffers&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Megan Jeffers (page does not exist)">Megan Jeffers</a> as Grace Jessup</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Bob_Balaban" title="Bob Balaban">Bob Balaban</a> as Arthur Rosenberg</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Charles_Haid" title="Charles Haid">Charles Haid</a> as Mason Parrish</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Thaao_Penghlis" title="Thaao Penghlis">Thaao Penghlis</a> as Eduardo Eccheverria</li>
<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Miguel_Godreau&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Miguel Godreau (page does not exist)">Miguel Godreau</a> as Primal Man</li>
<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Dori_Brenner&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Dori Brenner (page does not exist)">Dori Brenner</a> as Sylvia Rosenberg</li>
